# 🕵️ Investigation Steps

## 🔍 Identify Attacker IP

```bash
sudo grep "Failed password" /var/log/auth.log
```

---

## ✅ Check Successful Login

```bash
sudo grep "Accepted" /var/log/auth.log
```

---

## ⛔ Block Attacker IP

### Linux

```bash
sudo iptables -A INPUT -s 192.168.1.9 -j DROP
```

### Windows

```cmd
netsh advfirewall firewall add rule name="BLOCK-BRUTE" dir=in action=block remoteip=192.168.1.9
```

